| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2632 — Recovery Inhibition (blackbasta)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: aca1fc66-0ca7-5a70-9201-5fe40f0d4da0"
